description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an individual who has experience of managing a team and who has excellent interpersonal and IT skills. You must be organised and confident and able to work on your own initiative. You will need a friendly and approachable manner and have the ability to work under pressure in a changing environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our ideal candidate would be someone with experience as a Practice Manager or someone with administrative experience in Primary Care, perhaps previously working as an Assistant Practice Manager or Practice administrator.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are small single-handed dispensing GP surgery looking after just over 2600 patients in Holywell, North Wales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are offering a leadership post managing a small sized GMS practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will oversee the daily operations of the practice and supporting staff to deliver high quality services and to meet targets, supporting local achievement of National Service Frameworks, health improvement initiatives contracts, General Medical Services, ES, QOF and other areas agreed in response to the needs of the practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a part time post up to 18 hoursper week. Salary will be attractive/negotiable depending on the candidate’s experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Prospective candidates are welcome to call or visit the practice for an informal discussion about the position.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Person Specification&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Qualifications&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•GCSE grade A to C in English and Maths&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Human resources knowledge or experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•General Practice finance knowledge&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Small Business management experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Good experience of IT systems including Microsoft office&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Desirable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Practice Managers diploma or equivalent&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Educated to A level standard&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Management experience in general practice&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Experience of working in General Practice or a similar setting&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Desirable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Experience of VISION computer system&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;•Good communication skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Disclosure and Barring Service Check&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is subject to the Rehabilitation of Offenders Act (Exceptions Order) 1975 and as such it will be necessary for a submission for Disclosure to be made to the Disclosure and Barring Service (formerly known as CRB) to check for any previous criminal convictions.&lt;/p&gt;
